data.description: Eclectic style in one of St. Augustine's most established communities! Peaceful and quiet, tucked away on a beautiful lot with high elevation and fenced backyard! This private location offers a serene setting with stunning lake views, large open spaces and room for all the toys! Well maintained and ready for a new owners touch! The intelligent design provides and warm and comfortable flow with a split floor plan and multiple living areas. Unique and custom with colorful accents, galley kitchen and combo area dining room. Your enormous backyard is a wonderful place for enjoying the outdoors and soaking in the sun.  Plenty of room for a pool with a large side yard, perfect for storage or a trailer . Nicely constructed with added improvements over the life of the home.  Tasteful landscaping with a cool side-entry front door and air conditioned 1 car garage.  Decorative tile floors throughout the main living room with plank tile floors in the bedrooms. Give us a call for your private tour! Welcome to 251 Lily Road.  This charming home located in St. Augustine Shores is an attractive value in a spectacular location.  The Shores community offers a wide variety of community amenities, perfect for everyone! Winding streets, treed walk ways, tennis courts, open play areas, boat storage + so much more.  Nestled on the banks of the ICW, this amazing neighborhood is just minutes from historic downtown St. Augustine and the white sandy beaches on Anastasia Island.  Easy access to I-95 with all the modern conveniences just around the corner!
